ower to shape training programs, with the benefit of knowing their staff and surroundings. Our train-the-trainer package equips subject matter experts with everything they need to deliver engaging and effective training that meets regulatory standards and incorporates best practices. Our expertly crafted learning materials include up-to-date policies and are created by professionals with occupational experience and a <a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/blogs/dr-richard-dune/we-are-endorsed-by-skills-for-care" target="_blank"><i><span style="color: rgb(0, 102, 204);">Skills for Care endorsement</span></i></a>, demonstrating our unwavering commitment to providing high-quality training materials.<br><br>By sharing your expertise with others and developing the skills of your colleagues, you can make a tangible impact on the quality of care provided within your organisation. Furthermore, all of our train-the-trainer courses are <a href="https://cpduk.co.uk/providers/the-mandatory-training-group" target="_blank"><i><span style="color: rgb(0, 102, 204);">CPD-UK-accredited</span></i></a>, enabling you to embark on a journey of personal and professional development, enhancing your resume and opening doors to exciting career opportunities.</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-jeraig eTNnJl pf-70_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eTwdGJ utmwk pf-72_">Convenient training that keeps you compliant</span></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Convenient_training_that_keeps_you_compliant_-_Care_Certificate_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1692875395" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Convenient_training_that_keeps_you_compliant_-_Care_Certificate_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1692875395 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Convenient_training_that_keeps_you_compliant_-_Care_Certificate_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.jpg?v=1692875395 320w" width="1832" height